3	 *
4	 * Creates a PluginRegistry with all available plugins loaded,
5	 * then creates a SessionManager instance backed by core's implementation.
6	 * This ensures the CLI uses the same hash-based naming, metadata format,
7	 * and plugin abstractions as the rest of the system.
8	 */
